Wikipedia Lookup Pidgin Plugin

Building and Installation
-------------------------
First cd into source directory and  create a new directory. Now cd into the new
directory and run the following comands:

$ cmake ..
$ make

To install the plugin in Pidgin default directory (/user/.purple/plugins) run:

$ make install

Please notice, that the build-script is at work and might not work in some cases.
If that happens, please write a bug report or an mail. 


How to use
----------
First add the plugin (Tools->Plugins), call the Settings dialog and choose your 
preferred Wikipedia language.
Open a conversation window and type in a word. Now select the
word, open the context-menu (right-click) and choose menu entry
Wikipedia.

More functions coming soon. 


